snippet.title: Offensive Combat: Redux! - Melee Weapon - Rubber Chicken
snippet.description: Offensive Combat: Redux! (http://bit.ly/OCRedux) has the most realistic rubber chicken of any game, for your melee weapon pleasure.  Check out the game in beta now, and launching August 18, 2017.
